(27107, 'Smoflipid 20% emulsion 250ml i.v. inf.', 'سموفيليبيد 20% مستحلب 250 مل محلول وريدي', '', '169', 'Fish oil+olive oil+soya bean oil+triglyceride', 'Fresenius kabi', 'Unknown', 'غير محدد', 'محلول لدعم الصحة -- مصدر للسعرات الحرارية والاحماض الدهنية', '', '20%', 'Under FDA approval, fish oil pharmaceuticals are typically products consisting of a combination of the omega-3-fatty acids eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) and docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) and are indicated primarily as an adjunct to diet to reduce triglyceride levels in adult patients with severe (>=500 mg/dL) hypertriglyceridemia [FDA Label, F36].
